HEADWORD: Poikilothermic
<hw>Poi`ki*lo*ther"mic</hw> <pr>(-th⟦etil⟧r"m⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>poiki`los</grk> changeable + E. <ets>thermal</ets>, <ets>thermic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Having a varying body temperature. See <er>Homoiothermal</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
